title: MARX BROTHERS: THE MUSICAL COMPENDUM (second attempt)
description:
MARX BROTHERS: A Musical Compendium (2 hours)

Here's a compilation of the musical moments of the Marx Brothers
movies. I did it by myself and just for fun - all I want is to
help preserve the memory of the past and show the great entertainers
that were the Marx Brothers.
